<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9oW.0RR7SMrWCuOJAzYqeQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/RTHK-MTR-190910-09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9oW.0RR7SMrWCuOJAzYqeQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FRTHK-MTR-190910-09.jpg&h=2e8676e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林偉強︰港鐵應提早考慮封站<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】近日多個港鐵站設施遭破壞，香港鐵路工會聯合會主席林偉強認為，港鐵應提早考慮封站，保障乘客與員工安全。<br />\n<br />\n林偉強︰「如果發現路面運動有蔓延的趨勢，而且會有不能控制的情況，應該盡快考慮封站。因為封站要時間不是話封就封，而且當有暴徒進入車站就更加麻煩，所以最近封站都要警察幫忙。如果能早些封站，對站內不會再有乘客流轉，起碼會安全很多。」<br />\n<br />\n好辦法喎<br />\n不如直接拆左黨鐵咪唔洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:53:10.000Z","msg":"又係姓林既主席~~~"},{"pid":"dc102de86807ac84e0c68d2c057bf61d3e2f045c","tid":1556910,"uid":76988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9tL1LUe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9tL1LUe.png&h=af2b3245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48110dd985cf883a0f13e533e38a0f20d9f9cfb","tid":1556910,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:54:30.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n全部線一齊停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062348a054de2e7c17081c858fd220dead14a8b2","tid":1556910,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:55:13.000Z","msg":"唔駛咁煩啦<br />\n成條鐵執柒左佢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e654382249b7cb72049fa8d282aa4bfe00b1a589","tid":1556910,"uid":129243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T